data.description: Welcome home! This 4-bedroom, 2-bath tri-level residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Situated in a sought after neighborhood, this property boasts a range of sought-after features that make it an ideal choice for you and your family. Enjoy the convenience of a first-floor bedroom. Freshly painted rooms provide a clean and modern backdrop. An additional flex room adjacent to the screened porch is ready to become your home office, playroom, or serene reading nook. Step onto your deck and embrace the outdoor lifestyle. Located in a family-friendly community, you'll have access to great schools, parks, and local amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home.
